    "Furthermore, the software facilitates seamless navigation between visual mathematics options presented on diverse screens, enabling students to manipulate objects dynamically.",
    "As pointed out by Gono (2016), on-screen images can be enlarged, functions can be adapted, and colour coding can be employed.",
    "Numerous research studies conducted across various grade levels have consistently demonstrated the significant impact of GeoGebra on students' mathematics achievement, attitudes towards mathematics and long-term retention of knowledge (e.g.",
